{"tid":1722604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由呢一刻開始唔好再屌埋大","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:26:17.000Z","uid":97948,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7546a38df3cb47ea03c712a16288eeb1da417ea0","tid":1722604,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"由琴日屌到而家 越黎越多手足話唔幫埋大離開左<br />\n我呢幾日係暴大 琴日係埋大幫手 <br />\n我唔係冷氣軍師 絕對有資格講 埋大係有好多不足 <br />\n但結終好多冇實戰經驗 唔可以直接同暴大比<br />\n你地可以比意見 佢地再改變 <br />\n但唔好一黎就係咁屌佢地on9 <br />\n係咁分化話以後唔入去幫手<br />\n埋大係一個好重要既戰地 要守住紅隧<br />\n加上埋大易攻難守 入去既手足係有無比既勇氣<br />\n你地係咁屌只會令更多人唔入埋大幫手<br />\n分化割席不但幫唔到件事 仲會令手足失守同被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以由呢一刻開始唔該唔好再屌埋大<br />\n有需要就幫手 不分化不割席</span><br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"1d1c5bc826d307e3b9c84f01062afc1fe072d10d","tid":1722604,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7be1215b8c78cd347fe6878f6082a9f1641ded0","tid":1722604,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd5d232565f289bba77e91f4adab7a67e441bf30","tid":1722604,"uid":244749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bec23b6e5deac0f5c96442c2f34851d9cb53a19b","tid":1722604,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆，但要保持檢討比意見，一直進步"},{"pid":"26b01735ee1253d4a0476ac4e2ea837ccd3defce","tid":1722604,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真連登成晚勁多分化POST<br />\n手足我就一定唔屌嘅<br />\n上少D連登, 多D落去現場啦"},{"pid":"0aaf37d02561f163e6422b853628fb29f1ff5e10","tid":1722604,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b01735ee1253d4a0476ac4e2ea837ccd3defce","tid":1722604,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc